## ðŸ“Š CRISIS ASSESSMENT MATRIX

### Severity Classification
| Severity Level | Financial Impact | Operational Impact | Reputation Impact | Response Time |
|----------------|------------------|-------------------|-------------------|---------------|
| **Level 1 - Critical** | >$10M or >20% revenue | Complete shutdown | Major damage | Immediate |
| **Level 2 - High** | $1M-$10M or 5-20% revenue | Significant disruption | Moderate damage | <2 hours |
| **Level 3 - Medium** | $100K-$1M or 1-5% revenue | Limited disruption | Minor damage | <4 hours |
| **Level 4 - Low** | <$100K or <1% revenue | Minimal disruption | Negligible damage | <8 hours |

